      <title>加纳向投资者发行新债券，欧元债券摆脱违约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/ghana-eurobonds-exit-default-as-new-bonds-issued-to-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳向投资者发行新债券以换取现有债券，完成了漫长的重组过程，旨在使其贷款在国际货币基金组织计划下更加可持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/ghana-eurobonds-exit-default-as-new-bonds-issued-to-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 12:08:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
