    <item>
      <title>康菲石油公司获得美国许可，以偿还委内瑞拉债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/conocophillips-gets-us-licenses-in-bid-to-recoup-venezuela-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，康菲石油公司已获得美国政府的一系列许可，这些许可使这家石油和天然气生产商能够更好地收回委内瑞拉十多年前扣押和国有化其资产后欠下的部分或全部约 100 亿美元债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/conocophillips-gets-us-licenses-in-bid-to-recoup-venezuela-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行官员希望保留降息步伐的选择余地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/ecb-officials-wanted-to-keep-options-open-on-pace-of-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上次政策决定的记录显示，在通胀尚未完全得到抑制、欧元区经济面临风险不断加大的情况下，欧洲央行官员热衷于保持降息速度的灵活性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/ecb-officials-wanted-to-keep-options-open-on-pace-of-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cain Int'l 首席执行官谈房地产复苏、英国投资、切尔西足球俱乐部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-10/cain-int-l-ceo-on-real-estate-uk-investing-chelsea-fc-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cain International 首席执行官乔纳森·戈德斯坦 (Jonathan Goldstein) 讨论了欧洲房地产和投资前景，因为大多数发达国家的利率开始下降。Cain 出现在彭博电视的“与弗朗辛·拉夸一起脉搏”节目中。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-10/cain-int-l-ceo-on-real-estate-uk-investing-chelsea-fc-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:44:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前中国人民银行官员因受贿被判死缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/ex-pboc-official-gets-suspended-death-sentence-for-taking-bribes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一家法院对中国人民银行前副行长因收受贿赂逾 3.86 亿元人民币（5460 万美元）判处死缓。这一备受关注的案件体现了习近平主席整顿金融业的决心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/ex-pboc-official-gets-suspended-death-sentence-for-taking-bribes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:42:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
