    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚在标普上调利率后首次会议上维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/serbia-holds-rates-steady-in-first-meeting-after-s-p-upgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在巴尔干国家获得投资级评级后，塞尔维亚决策者在首次会议上维持利率不变，理由是地缘政治风险和夏季干旱的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/serbia-holds-rates-steady-in-first-meeting-after-s-p-upgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 10:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克通胀高于预期，加重降息谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/czech-inflation-exceeds-forecasts-as-central-bank-flags-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国上个月的通货膨胀率超出预期，这进一步增加了央行对降息保持谨慎态度的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/czech-inflation-exceeds-forecasts-as-central-bank-flags-caution</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 07:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
